    public static class SemanticRestriction.DataDomainRestrictedOnExactData
extends SemanticRestriction.ApplyingDataExactRestriction<org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLDataProperty,org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLDataPropertyDomainAxiom>
implements SemanticRestriction.RestrictOnDataPropertyDomain<org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLDataRange>
    This class combines SemanticRestriction.ApplyingDataExactRestriction with the SemanticRestriction.RestrictOnDataPropertyDomain interface in order to define a restriction of a data property domain within an exact number of data properties in a given data type. It set the SemanticRestriction.ApplyingRestriction.restrictionType to SemanticRestriction.RestrictionType.DATA_DOMAIN_EXACT_DATA. It does not implement any further features rather than the constructors, see the above classes for more details.
